作家[[冰心|冰心]]表示完全欽佩：“周恩來總理是我國二十世紀的十億人民心目中的第一位完人。”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://lit.eastday.com/renda/node5661/node5667/userobject1ai1285264.html |title=[[趙麗宏|趙麗宏]]，冰心有贈. |access-date=2014-01-13 |archive-date=2014-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219121300/http://lit.eastday.com/renda/node5661/node5667/userobject1ai1285264.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

